column1: Daily Weather Observations for Launceston, Tasmania for June 2024
Prepared at 13:03 UTC on Tuesday  5 November 2024   IDCJDW7025.202406
Most observations from Ti Tree Bend, but pressure and cloud from the airport.

Conditions at Launceston Airport may be markedly different to those in the city on some days. Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
Temperature, humidity, wind, pressure and rainfall observations are from Launceston (Ti Tree Bend) {station 091237}
Cloud observations are from Launceston Airport {station 091311}
